- More optimizations -- can these all be done on the public API?
   - constant propagation
   - strength reduction
   - dedup / global value numbering via hash table
   - canonically sort arguments to symmetrical ops to help them dedup more
   - dead code elimination
   - loop invariant hoisting -- run uniform computation once, then loop over varyings

- New backends: arm64 JIT, Metal?

- Some limited form of uniform control flow, arguments and return values for
  basic blocks, calls from one program to another.

- Design graphics pipeline that uses these programs for both coverage and color.
